, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago

, max(c.initials), ' '

, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a

[2020-07-18 08:22:41.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->NORTIZ] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago

, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a

LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago

, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a

LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac

, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-07-18 09:37:50.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->NORTIZ] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago

, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-07-18 10:35:08.000000 192.130.74.30  - [query->CRIVERA] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-07-18 10:38:11.000000 192.130.74.30  - [query->CRIVERA] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-07-18 12:08:57.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->NORTIZ] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

union

order by id

[2020-07-18 12:31:54.000000 192.130.74.39  - [query->ADMINCITAS] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='2020-07-18' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-07-18 13:01:58.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->NORTIZ] ] Select 'Todos' as Descripcion, 1 as id  
union  
select 'Consultas' as Descripcion, 2 as id  
union  
select 'Sueroterapia' as Descripcion, 3 as id  
union  
select 'Laser' as Descripcion, 4 as id  
union 
select 'Intravenoso' as Descripcion, 5 as id  
union 
select 'Bloqueo' as Descripcion, 6 as id  
union 
select 'Celulas Madres' as Descripcion, 7 as id  
order by id

[2020-07-18 13:02:01.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->NORTIZ] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='7/18/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac
